体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">二○○六年三月</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">总<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span>则</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第一条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">为了规范地震科学数据共享系统的运行工作，加强对地震科学数据共享系统运行管理，充分发挥地震科学数据的作用，依据《地震科学数据共享管理办法》（中国地震局局长令第<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span>号），制定本规定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第二条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">地震科学数据共享系统由</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">国家地震科学数据共享中心和各分中心的运行系统组成<span style=\"color: black\">。</span>本规定适用于国家地震科学数据共享中心和各分中心的日常运行管理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第三条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">运行机制<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">3.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">国家地震科学数据共享中心在中国地震台网中心领导下开展日常运行工作；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">3.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">地震科学数据共享分中心在所在单位的领导下开展日常运行工作，接受国家地震科学数据共享中心的业务管理和技术指导；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">3.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">国家地震科学数据共享系统运行工作接受中国地震局信息学科技术协调组的指导。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">3.4 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">国家共享中心和分中心建立各自的数据服务网站，并提供以国家地震科学数据共享中心网站为门户网站的分类分级地震科学数据服务<span lang=\"EN-US\">.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第二章<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span>运行条件</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">第四条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">国家地震科学数据共享中心运行的基础条件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">4.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">具备至少<span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span>平米以上的独立工作场所和机房，具备必要的网络相关设备、数据库服务器、<span lang=\"EN-US\">WEB</span>服务器、大容量数据存储设备和其它必要设施，关键设备具有必要的备份<span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 1cm; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">4.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">具备至少<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" tcsc=\"0\" numbertype=\"1\" negative=\"False\" hasspace=\"False\" sourcevalue=\"10\" unitname=\"m\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">10M</span></st1:chmetcnv><span lang=\"EN-US\">/bps</span>以上至公众信息网的<span lang=\"EN-US\">INTERNET</span>出口带宽，并提供必要的网络安全保障措施<span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 1cm; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">4.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">具备大型数据库管理系统<span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 1cm; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">4.4 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">服务器和网络能力应至少满足<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>个并发用户查询、浏览、下载数据的需要<span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"marg