ow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第四章<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span>日常运行</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第十条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">运行规章制度<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">10.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">必须制定并遵循以下基本规章制度开展日常运行工作：①机房管理制度、②值班制度、③系统维护制度、④运行操作规程、⑤技术档案管理制度；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">10.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">设立专门的系统管理员，建立超级用户管理制度；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">10.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">设立专门的数据管理岗位<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>负责汇交数据公告发布、数据服务信息发布、汇交数据入库，并建立数据档案等工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第十一条</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"> 日常运行要求<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">11.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">值班员每日按规定巡视数据共享技术系统（网站、网络和数据库平台）的运行状态，按规定如实填写系统运行日志； <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28.5pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">11.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">系统管理员负责对数据共享技术系统的常规维护和故障处理，如实填写维护日志及维修记录；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28.5pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">11.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">国家地震科学数据共享中心对分中心的联通、运行状态实施定期检测，并及时通报情况；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28.5pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">11.4 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">系统管理值班手机必须<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>小时处于通讯状态，接到故障报告立即到岗；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">11.5 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">不得随意人为停止设备运行，正常的设备维护需停机<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>小时以上或发生重大故障造成系统停机，必须及时向有关管理部门报告，并向用户作出通告说明；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第十二条 </span></b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">数据服务<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">12.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">以&ldquo;安全、方便&rdquo;为原则，确定各类数据的备份方案，并严格执行数据备份方案； <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">12.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">根据<span style=\"color: black\">《</span>地震科学数据服务规定<span style=\"color: black\">》</span>的相关条款更新数据，并提供数据服务，做好用户登记和统一注册及其信息管理；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">12.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">国家地震科学数据共享中心应建立分中心数据更新档案，及时发布数据更新信息； <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">12.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">收集用户需求意见，根据用户需求提出完善数据服务系统的建议。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第十三条 </span></b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">运行月报编报<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28.5pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">13.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">编报运行月报。运行月报主要包含共享技术平台运行质量、数据汇交情况、数据更新情况、数据服务情况、用户需求与工作建议等内容；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28.5pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">13.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">分中心中心每月<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>日前向国家地震科学数据中心报送上月运行月报；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28.5pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">13.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">国家地震科学数据共享中心每月<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>日前向中国地震局数据共享主管部门报送上月系统运行月报。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">第十四条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">国家地震科学数据共享中心、分中心应制订应急工作预案，对网络黑客攻击、病毒攻击、数据盗取、网站故障恢复等相关事宜做出应急处置规定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">第五章<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span>运行评价</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体;