: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"宋体\">3.3<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">二级用户<span lang=\"EN-US\"> Second-class user</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"22ndlevelh22header2h2l2donotuseh2chnchapter2\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm; line-height: 150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"宋体\">3.4<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">数据发布<span lang=\"EN-US\"> data release</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">通过网站、报刊、广播、电视和电话等各种新闻媒体和通信工具对社会公众宣布有关方面信息的服务活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; line-height: 150%; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">发布主体与对象<span 